summary: I am an experienced researcher and team leader. Together with my research group, I work on understanding the spatiotemporal variability of renewable generation and on quantifying the technical, economic and political trade-offs between different possible ways to build a 100% clean and renewable energy system. I am also a software developer with particular expertise in scientific Python and in full stack web development, and lead development of the www.callio.pe and www.renewables.ninja projects.
